1
00:01:42,360 --> 00:01:43,120
Why?

2
00:01:44,360 --> 00:01:45,280
Li Yunxi.

3
00:01:46,160 --> 00:01:47,560
We were husband and wife.

4
00:01:48,160 --> 00:01:49,720
Why must you kill us all?

5
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:51,320
Your Majesty,

6
00:01:51,320 --> 00:01:53,920
the Empress has arrived outside Donghua Gate.

7
00:01:59,200 --> 00:02:01,320
If you want to fight on the battlefield,

8
00:02:01,320 --> 00:02:02,320
I won't stop you.

9
00:02:02,880 --> 00:02:04,680
If you want to defend the country,

10
00:02:04,680 --> 00:02:05,440
then go.

11
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:07,400
I will not stop you.

12
00:02:08,199 --> 00:02:09,530
I, Li Yunxi, swear here,

13
00:02:10,199 --> 00:02:11,460
for the rest of my life.

14
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:13,600
I will only have you.

15
00:02:14,200 --> 00:02:16,260
I have already stepped aside for you.

16
00:02:16,320 --> 00:02:18,280
Why can't you set me free?

17
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:19,720
His Majesty decrees,

18
00:02:19,760 --> 00:02:22,490
to prevent the Empress from escaping the palace,

19
00:02:22,560 --> 00:02:24,040
sever her hand tendons

20
00:02:27,480 --> 00:02:28,480
and foot tendons.

21
00:02:30,840 --> 00:02:32,240
Only when you die

22
00:02:32,320 --> 00:02:34,040
can I become Empress.

23
00:02:34,880 --> 00:02:36,280
Even if I die...

24
00:02:37,079 --> 00:02:38,800
I won't stay here.

25
00:02:39,680 --> 00:02:41,480
Even if we torment each other,

26
00:02:42,680 --> 00:02:44,610
we will be together for a lifetime.

27
00:02:52,160 --> 00:02:53,720
Li Yunxi is marrying you

28
00:02:54,160 --> 00:02:55,560
because he wants your father's command

29
00:02:55,560 --> 00:02:57,440
of the 30,000 Xiao Army.

30
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:14,040
My mother gave me this jade pendant.

31
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:15,420
If you put it on,

32
00:03:16,360 --> 00:03:18,560
you can never take it off, even in death.

33
00:03:18,720 --> 00:03:19,200
Okay.

34
00:03:32,480 --> 00:03:33,240
Where am I?

35
00:03:33,760 --> 00:03:35,040
Is this the Underworld?

36
00:03:35,040 --> 00:03:35,970
This incense...

37
00:03:46,920 --> 00:03:47,960
Is this a dream?

38
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:50,440
Why does it feel so real?

39
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:00,840
Have I been reborn?

40
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:13,080
Your Highness, go!

41
00:04:16,040 --> 00:04:16,839
Leave me!

42
00:04:17,279 --> 00:04:18,279
Go!

43
00:04:23,600 --> 00:04:25,000
Your Highness, I'm sorry.

44
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:25,860
I was careless.

45
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:28,400
Hanxing,

46
00:04:30,640 --> 00:04:31,400
Hanxing,

47
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:34,250
you're still alive.

48
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:42,659
Your Highness,

49
00:04:43,240 --> 00:04:44,640
did you have a nightmare?

50
00:04:46,320 --> 00:04:48,250
Was everything that just happened

51
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:50,400
just a dream?

52
00:04:51,159 --> 00:04:51,960
Your Majesty,

53
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:54,520
His Majesty is hosting a palace banquet at Qinghuan Pavilion tonight.

54
00:04:54,520 --> 00:04:55,360
Please attend

55
00:04:56,400 --> 00:04:57,530
the palace banquet.

56
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:07,720
My Lady.

57
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:12,280
What's wrong?

58
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:14,360
I am feeling unwell.

59
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:16,130
I will take my leave.

60
00:05:21,760 --> 00:05:22,600
Li Yunxi.

61
00:05:25,080 --> 00:05:26,200
You promised me

62
00:05:26,960 --> 00:05:27,960
that in this life,

63
00:05:28,640 --> 00:05:30,080
you would only marry me.

64
00:05:31,280 --> 00:05:32,640
How could you lie to me?

65
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:35,640
Please don't leave me.

66
00:05:38,360 --> 00:05:40,290
You are my husband, and mine alone.

67
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:01,440
Where is my jade pendant?

68
00:06:03,240 --> 00:06:04,240
Why is it you?

69
00:06:11,280 --> 00:06:12,340
What are you doing?

70
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:22,000
You betrayed me.

71
00:06:22,520 --> 00:06:23,520
You betrayed Us.

72
00:06:25,640 --> 00:06:26,400
I didn't.

73
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:36,120
From today on,

74
00:06:37,920 --> 00:06:40,320
you are not allowed to step out of Jile Hall.

75
00:06:41,200 --> 00:06:42,400
His Majesty decrees,

76
00:06:43,040 --> 00:06:45,770
to prevent the Empress from escaping the palace,

77
00:06:46,159 --> 00:06:47,640
sever her hand tendons

78
00:06:48,960 --> 00:06:50,000
and foot tendons.

79
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:55,240
So Consort Xue is behind this.

80
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:58,440
Change clothes. Go to the banquet.

81
00:06:59,880 --> 00:07:02,600
Her Majesty the Empress arrives.

82
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:10,440
We could have lived our own happy lives.

83
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:12,800
But you forced me into a dead end.

84
00:07:14,200 --> 00:07:16,530
Since Heaven has given me a second chance,

85
00:07:17,560 --> 00:07:18,400
then let's see

86
00:07:18,520 --> 00:07:20,450
who will truly emerge victorious.

87
00:07:21,240 --> 00:07:22,770
And who will come out on top.

88
00:07:24,640 --> 00:07:27,040
Prince Qi, Li Yunmo. The Emperor's cousin.

89
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:31,120
The good brother who fought beside me on the battlefield.

90
00:07:31,400 --> 00:07:32,930
Consort Xue, Liu Mianmian.

91
00:07:33,640 --> 00:07:35,640
The Emperor's favorite concubine.

92
00:07:35,840 --> 00:07:38,440
The one in the palace who could not tolerate me.

93
00:07:39,360 --> 00:07:40,360
Li Yunxi.

94
00:07:40,960 --> 00:07:42,360
Five years of affection,

95
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:44,380
two years of marriage.

96
00:07:45,159 --> 00:07:47,220
You actually had the heart to kill me.

97
00:07:49,240 --> 00:07:51,440
Don't even think about leaving my side.

98
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:53,920
Even if we torture each other,

99
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:56,960
we will be together for a lifetime.

100
00:08:06,880 --> 00:08:08,680
I propose a toast to Your Majesty

101
00:08:08,960 --> 00:08:10,280
and the Empress.

102
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:22,200
Good wine.

103
00:08:29,200 --> 00:08:30,060
Your Highness,

104
00:08:33,559 --> 00:08:34,360
what's wrong?

105
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:37,280
I'm not feeling well.

106
00:08:38,559 --> 00:08:39,760
I shall take my leave.

107
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:50,600
Your Majesty, I shall take my leave.

108
00:09:00,520 --> 00:09:01,680
Don't worry, Your Majesty.

109
00:09:01,680 --> 00:09:02,640
Someone reported

110
00:09:02,640 --> 00:09:05,170
that the Empress has returned to Jile Palace.

111
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:07,480
A-Ling left the banquet,

112
00:09:07,480 --> 00:09:08,680
and Li Yunmo left too.

113
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:10,360
I think Li Yunmo is just relying on

114
00:09:10,360 --> 00:09:12,880
having been A-Ling's comrade on the battlefield for years

115
00:09:12,880 --> 00:09:14,410
to plot something illicit.

116
00:09:23,720 --> 00:09:24,800
Liu Mianmian.

117
00:09:27,600 --> 00:09:28,400
Your Majesty.

118
00:09:29,760 --> 00:09:30,560
Your Majesty.

119
00:09:31,520 --> 00:09:32,840
I missed you so much.

120
00:09:33,120 --> 00:09:35,400
Please don't push me away tonight.

121
00:09:41,880 --> 00:09:43,080
What did you do to her?

122
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:45,240
I merely returned the wine

123
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:46,600
Concubine Xue gave me

124
00:09:47,480 --> 00:09:48,360
to her.

125
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:02,520
Since you want to play,

126
00:10:03,520 --> 00:10:05,280
I'll play along.

127
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:08,720
You mean

128
00:10:09,680 --> 00:10:10,840
she framed you?

129
00:10:11,160 --> 00:10:13,080
If Your Majesty doesn't believe me,

130
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:15,160
then consider that I used her gift

131
00:10:15,760 --> 00:10:18,020
to bring you and Concubine Xue together.

132
00:10:21,600 --> 00:10:23,600
This is my Palace of Ultimate Bliss.

133
00:10:23,760 --> 00:10:25,800
If you want to neutralize the Qingsirao,

134
00:10:25,800 --> 00:10:27,360
please take Concubine Xue

135
00:10:27,520 --> 00:10:28,980
back to her Feixue Palace.

136
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:32,060
Why is there Qingsirao in the palace?

137
00:10:34,240 --> 00:10:36,640
You'll have to ask your beloved concubine.

138
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:38,800
Your Majesty.

139
00:10:50,240 --> 00:10:51,080
Li Yunxi.

140
00:10:51,880 --> 00:10:54,440
The show has just begun.
